SchemeName.Name: RO:Lista furnizorilor de servicii de certificare digitale calificate, care sunt supravegheati/acreditati in conformitate cu Directiva 1999/93/EC si cu legile nationale.

RO:Supervision/Accreditation Status List of certification services from Certification Service Providers, which are supervised/accredited by the referenced Scheme Operator’s Member State for compliance with the relevant provisions laid down in Directive 1999/93/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 13 December 1999 on a Community framework for electronic signatures.

PolicyOrLegalNotice.TSLLegalNotice: The applicable legal framework for the present TSL implementation of the Trusted List of supervised/accredited Certification Service Providers for Romania is Directive 1999/93/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 13 December 1999 on a Community framework for electronic signatures and its implementation in Romanian laws.

Cadrul legal aplicabil pentru punerea în aplicare a prezentei Liste de încredere a Furnizorilor de servicii de certificare supravegheati/acreditati pentru România este Directiva 1999/93/CE a Parlamentului European şi a Consiliului din 13 decembrie 1999 privind un cadru comunitar pentru semnăturile electronice şi de transpunerea sa in legile romanesti.
